CBRE is pleased to be exclusively appointed on the sale of 29-31 Waldheim Road, Bayswater. 

The property presents a significant landholding which has dual street access to Waldheim Road and Ricdanic Drive. The low site coverage allows owner occupiers or developers future expansion (STCA) or ample hardstand/yard all within 2.6km* of M3 Eastlink.

Surrounding local occupiers include Confoil, Camerons Transport, and Emerson Automation Solutions.

Location Details:
+ M3 Eastlink 2.6km*
+ Mountain Highway 111m*
+ Stud Road 175m*
+ Bayswater Railway Station 1.67km*
+ Westfield Knox 2.95km*

Property Details:
+ Offered with vacant possession
+ Industrial 1 Zone
+ Total building area 4,788sqm*
+ Total land area 14,631sqm*
+ Dual street frontages to Waldheim Road and Ricdanic Drive

For further information on the sale of 29-31 Waldheim Road please contact exclusive marketing agents Joe Brzezek or Sasan Misaghian from CBRE.

*approx.

* Substantial Industrial 1 zoned parcel - 9,508sqm
* Modern, well-maintained and highly functional office building - 540sqm
* Existing industrial facility or factory/warehouse - 3,200sqm
* Eight (8) overhead cranes (two 12 tonne and two 5 tonne) and integrated spray booth
* Original building provides 12m clearance (9m under hook)
* Massive power supply
* Excellent hardstand /marshalling area
* Full drive-thru/around capability
* Car parking for 60-70 vehicles

* Prime, tightly-held eastern suburbs industrial location
* Established industrial precinct well serviced by a network of major arterials including Canterbury Road, Dorset Road, Maroondah Highway and Mountain Highway. Efficient access to Eastlink Tollway

5/640 Dorset Road represents an excellent opportunity to lease a well presented office warehouse in the tightly held Bayswater industrial precinct. The site has is situated off Dorset Road which provides access to major surrounding arterial roads including East Link and Canterbury Road. 

Property Highlights include:
- Warehouse 3,600sqm*
- High internal clearance
- Multiple roller shutter doors (3) 
- Ample Hardstand 
- Access to main surrounding arterials.
